    <item>
      <title>iTunes First Time User Welcome Messages</title>
      <link>http://konigi.com/interface/itunes-first-time-user-welcome-messages/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Sep 2009 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://konigi.com/interface/itunes-first-time-user-welcome-messages/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;First time users of iTunes are presented with instruction screens for adding media to their library. The simple instruction panels provide links to buy media or to watch video tutorials showing how to purchase, import, and use the software.&lt;/p&gt;
