      <link>http://konigi.com/interface/sling-welcome-message/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Dec 2008 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://konigi.com/interface/sling-welcome-message/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Sling.com&#39;s welcome message position&#39;s a 3 column intro to the site for first time users, which it positions between the main promo marquee and the body of the page. Dismiss the message as a logged in user and it shouldn&#39;t come back again.&lt;/p&gt;
